{"content": "I need to multiply 505 \u00d7 717 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 505\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 0 + 5\u00d71 = 405 + 0 + 5 = 410\u2081\u2080\n- 717\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 7\u00d71 = 567 + 9 + 7 = 583\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 410 \u00d7 583 = 239,030\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 239030 \u00f7 9 = 26558 r 8\n- 26558 \u00f7 9 = 2950 r 8\n- 2950 \u00f7 9 = 327 r 7\n- 327 \u00f7 9 = 36 r 3\n- 36 \u00f7 9 = 4 r 0\n- 4 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 4\n\nReading from bottom to top: **403788\u2089**\n\n403788", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 342}